high_descs: Turn to your right and walk towards the kitchen sink, then make a right at the kitchen sink and walk to the garbage can at the end of the counter, on your left.
Remove a green and yellow sponge from the garbage can.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn right and go to the stove.
Put the sponge in the pan on the front, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside, from the front, right burner of the stove.
Turn to your right and walk across the kitchen, to the sink.
Place the pan with the sponge inside, in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a sponge in the sink.

high_descs: turn right and walk towards the sink. make a right to walk towards the window. turn left at the trash can
pick up the green object from the trash
turn left and take a few steps. turn left again and walk towards the wall.  turn right and walk over to the stove
place the object in the pot
pick up the pot from the stove
turn right and walk over to the sink
place the pot in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a green object inside in the sink

high_descs: Turn right, walk past the two tables on both sides, turn left towards the window, and turn left to find a black in on the floor.
Take a green sponge out of the bin.
Turn left, take a few steps straight towards the sink, turn left and walk to the stove on your right.
Place the sponge on the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the sponge.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the pan along with the green sponge from the bin into the sink.
